## 3. Mẫu Driver — GPIO Interrupt (YF-S201 style)

Dùng cho cảm biến tạo xung (encoder, flow meter, hall effect...).

### Nguyên tắc ISR

```c
// 1. Biến volatile cho ISR + mutex/protect
static volatile uint32_t s_pulse_count = 0;
static portMUX_TYPE s_pulse_mutex = portMUX_INITIALIZER_UNLOCKED;

// 2. ISR handler — IRAM_ATTR bắt buộc
static void IRAM_ATTR pulse_isr(void *arg) {
    portENTER_CRITICAL_ISR(&s_pulse_mutex);
    s_pulse_count++;
    portEXIT_CRITICAL_ISR(&s_pulse_mutex);
}

// 3. Init
gpio_config_t io_conf = {
    .pin_bit_mask = (1ULL << PIN),
    .mode = GPIO_MODE_INPUT,
    .pull_up_en = GPIO_PULLUP_ENABLE,
    .intr_type = GPIO_INTR_POSEDGE,  // Hoặc NEGEDGE tùy cảm biến
};
gpio_config(&io_conf);
gpio_install_isr_service(ESP_INTR_FLAG_IRAM);
gpio_isr_handler_add(PIN, pulse_isr, NULL);
```

### Đọc an toàn từ Task

```c
static uint32_t get_and_reset_count(void) {
    uint32_t count;
    portENTER_CRITICAL(&s_pulse_mutex);
    count = s_pulse_count;
    s_pulse_count = 0;
    portEXIT_CRITICAL(&s_pulse_mutex);
    return count;
}
```

