## 6. Mẫu Driver — ADC (GSR style)

```c
// 1. Init ADC
adc_oneshot_unit_init_cfg_t init_cfg = {
    .unit_id = ADC_UNIT_1,
    .ulp_mode = ADC_ULP_MODE_DISABLE,
};
ESP_ERROR_CHECK(adc_oneshot_new_unit(&init_cfg, &handle));

// 2. Config channel
adc_oneshot_chan_cfg_t cfg = {
    .bitwidth = ADC_BITWIDTH_DEFAULT,
    .atten = ADC_ATTEN_DB_12,
};
ESP_ERROR_CHECK(adc_oneshot_config_channel(handle, channel, &cfg));

// 3. Đọc nhiều mẫu + trung bình
long sum = 0;
for (int i = 0; i < SAMPLE_SIZE; i++) {
    int val;
    adc_oneshot_read(handle, channel, &val);
    sum += val;
    vTaskDelay(pdMS_TO_TICKS(2));
}
int raw = sum / SAMPLE_SIZE;
```

